15 SECTION 1. AMENDATORY Section 2, Chapter 151, O.S.L.
16 2022 (36 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section 6060.41), is amended to read as
17 follows:
18 Section 6060.41. As used in the Oklahoma Right to Shop Act:
19 1. "Allowed amount" means the contractually agreed-upon amount
20 paid by a carrier to a health care entity participating in the
21 network of the carrier;
22 2. "Average allowed amount" means the mean of all allowed
23 amounts paid for a comparable health care service;
24
